    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010130/extras/496d0eebddae7bd1ccffce9d000fae76.avif?t=1761569485\" width=750 height=168 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the chaos in <strong><i>Monster Mayhem</i></strong>! Cute little monsters go head-to-head in wild races, team battles, and all sorts of different challenges. Grab your friends, dive into the madness, and see who will take home the most trophies to become the ultimate Monster Champion!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Party game</strong> for 2–8 players,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete across multiple rounds to get the most <strong>trophies </strong>and win it all,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tons of <strong>customization </strong>options to make your monster your own</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010130/extras/6262842f24c735d029a29c9b79c453a0.webp?t=1761569485\" width=750 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010130/extras/023b283ede9649eef55897f16b71b923.avif?t=1761569485\" width=750 height=168 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete in various Minigames! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reach the end of our <strong>Race Games</strong> first, stay alive in our <strong>Survival Games</strong> the longest or lead your team to victory in our <strong>Sports Games</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010130/extras/909f6a00a24d677429e0dc70beaa863b.poster.avif?t=1761569485\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010130/extras/909f6a00a24d677429e0dc70beaa863b.webm?t=1761569485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010130/extras/909f6a00a24d677429e0dc70beaa863b.mp4?t=1761569485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010130/extras/6262842f24c735d029a29c9b79c453a0.webp?t=1761569485\" width=750 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010130/extras/23e0883051c7e962976df18f33c9bb0b.avif?t=1761569485\" width=750 height=168 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from plenty different customization options! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Personalize your little monster with different <strong>Colors</strong>, <strong>Patterns</strong> and <strong>Hats</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010130/extras/4fade922ffd2165a5daae517364f4fe0.avif?t=1761569485\" width=1560 height=822 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010130/extras/ccb1bcde5ee38f5cf2975deb28785852.poster.avif?t=1761569485\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010130/extras/ccb1bcde5ee38f5cf2975deb28785852.webm?t=1761569485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010130/extras/ccb1bcde5ee38f5cf2975deb28785852.mp4?t=1761569485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010130/extras/6262842f24c735d029a29c9b79c453a0.webp?t=1761569485\" width=750 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010130/extras/912487c5e683674a039eda90a8cdc867.avif?t=1761569485\" width=750 height=168 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy our beautiful scenery! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different <strong>Biomes</strong> (Grasslands, Forest, Desert and more!) will give you a diverse experience and each map has its own unique Theme!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010130/extras/0f523c63c63b31e169ba45c9e7bd663d.poster.avif?t=1761569485\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010130/extras/0f523c63c63b31e169ba45c9e7bd663d.webm?t=1761569485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010130/extras/6262842f24c735d029a29c9b79c453a0.webp?t=1761569485\" width=750 height=30 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010130/extras/d65db4e7cbb8788a45348421a831986c.avif?t=1761569485\" width=750 height=168 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010130/extras/5508b070b3fd63ff2f8e5758e823eae5.poster.avif?t=1761569485\" width=850 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010130/extras/5508b070b3fd63ff2f8e5758e823eae5.webm?t=1761569485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010130/extras/5508b070b3fd63ff2f8e5758e823eae5.mp4?t=1761569485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010130/extras/6262842f24c735d029a29c9b79c453a0.webp?t=1761569485\" width=750 height=30 /></span></p>",
